NAME
    POE::Loop::IO_Async - IO::Async event loop support for POE

VERSION
    version 0.004

SYNOPSIS
    See POE::Loop.

DESCRIPTION
    POE::Loop::IO_Async implements the interface documented in POE::Loop.
    Therefore it has no documentation of its own. Please see POE::Loop for
    more details.

SEE ALSO
    POE

    POE::Loop

    IO::Async

